{"tid":333970,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩慘得過屋企人痾屎唔洗手","createTime":"2017-07-24T10:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T18:51:46.000Z","uid":77724,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df2a092ff8c028947dcf7e60fd69084a36b469f5","tid":333970,"uid":77724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:06:49.000Z","msg":"但你又唔話得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩聽到老豆係廁所坐左一輪，沖完廁所水即開門，<br />\n所以我平時都係洗完手再開門再洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屋企仲有個係我心目中幼稚園未畢業嘅阿哥廁所板都唔識拎起就痾尿，搞到廁板成日有尿，鼻涕周圍噴，試過沖涼房個水龍頭吊撚住條鼻涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114d850ae98ec6ff9ef92a68eceff45544611b5b","tid":333970,"uid":53126,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"唔怪得你阿媽唔比你養貓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b21f7fbab5423e753b7ee779d0427066597294b","tid":333970,"uid":77724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔怪得你阿媽唔比你養貓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dbc4acfa7053999a79d608fc517abc25308dec","tid":333970,"uid":28277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"佢地岩岩大陸落來？"},{"pid":"99979cbe3d981925edcb146e5c804daa238761f3","tid":333970,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"老豆都係咁 好撚on9<br />\n所以細細個已經唔聽佢講野"},{"pid":"eeb348b43c14f521550df53fe8d34c9baabba635","tid":333970,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11: